    187          /***************************************************************************//**
    188           * @brief
    189           *   Initialize IADC.
    190           *
    191           * @details
    192           *   Initializes common parts for both single conversion and scan sequence.
    193           *   In addition, single and/or scan control configuration must be done, please
    194           *   refer to @ref IADC_initSingle() and @ref IADC_initScan() respectively.
    195           *
    196           * @note
    197           *   This function will stop any ongoing conversions.
    198           *
    199           * @param[in] iadc
    200           *   Pointer to IADC peripheral register block.
    201           *
    202           * @param[in] init
    203           *   Pointer to IADC initialization structure.
    204           *
    205           * @param[in] allConfigs
    206           *   Pointer to structure holding all configs.
    207           ******************************************************************************/

   \                                 In section .text, align 4, keep-with-next
